- Miss, come. I'll take you to your room.
- I said I don't want to!

57
00:06:24,675 --> 00:06:28,786
- Miss! Miss, please don't!
- Daddy! Daddy, help me!

58
00:06:29,167 --> 00:06:30,919
Miss Carmelita, please don't be too loud.

59
