Miss, you are too drunk. You need to rest.

62
00:06:38,526 --> 00:06:40,075
Come, let's go.

63
00:06:40,852 --> 00:06:42,379
- I said no!
- But Miss...

64
00:06:43,229 --> 00:06:47,525
Miss Carmelita, you need
to get some rest. You--

65
